381
00:23:49.509 --> 00:23:50.476
- Oh. right.
- Thank you.

382
00:23:50.610 --> 00:23:51.779
- There you go.

383
00:23:51.912 --> 00:23:52.813
Oops.

384
00:23:55.382 --> 00:23:56.784
