414
00:25:48.797 --> 00:25:50.899
- You have a go. Emmy.

415
00:25:51.032 --> 00:25:51.933
- Okay.

416
00:26:04.813 --> 00:26:05.914
- I like that a lot.

417
00:26:06.247 --> 00:26:07.082
