451
00:28:40.637 --> 00:28:42.072
- You enjoying this?

452
00:28:42.205 --> 00:28:43.206
- Very nice.

453
00:28:43.340 --> 00:28:44.708
- More than the other night.

454
00:28:49.346 --> 00:28:53.550
